Label: DataCenter
Description: Represents data centers, primarily NASA DAACs, as well as other data providers in academia and government who manage and distribute datasets.

Label: Dataset
Description: Represents individual satellite datasets and data collections managed and distributed by NASA data centers and other providers worldwide.

Label: Instrument
Description: Represents scientific instruments and sensors used on satellites and platforms to collect Earth observation data.

Label: Platform
Description: Represents satellites, spacecraft, and other platforms that carry scientific instruments for data collection.

Label: Project
Description: Represents scientific missions and research projects associated with data collection and satellite operations.

Label: Publication
Description: Represents scientific publications and research papers that cite or utilize datasets from the knowledge graph.

Label: ScienceKeyword
Description: Represents scientific keywords and terms used to categorize and describe datasets by their sphere of application and research domain.

Label: date
Description: A point or period of time associated with an event in the lifecycle of the resource (Dublin Core Terms).

Label: identifier
Description: An unambiguous reference to the resource within a given context (Dublin Core Terms).

Label: subject
Description: The topic of the resource, typically represented using keywords or classification codes (Dublin Core Terms).

Label: label
Description: A human-readable name or label for the resource (RDF Schema).

Label: year
Description: Represents a year in the Gregorian calendar (OWL Time Ontology).

Label: CITES
Description: Represents citation relationships between Publication nodes, indicating how research builds on previous work.

Label: cmrId
Description: The Common Metadata Repository identifier for a dataset in NASA's data management system.

Label: daac
Description: Identifies the Distributed Active Archive Center (DAAC) responsible for archiving and distributing the dataset.

Label: globalId
Description: A globally unique identifier for the resource across the knowledge graph.

Label: HAS_APPLIEDRESEARCHAREA
Description: Associates a Publication with a ScienceKeyword representing its research domain or application area.

Label: HAS_DATASET
Description: Connects a DataCenter to its Dataset(s), indicating which data center manages and distributes specific datasets.

Label: HAS_INSTRUMENT
Description: Connects a Platform to an Instrument, indicating which instruments are carried by a specific platform or satellite.

Label: HAS_PLATFORM
Description: Associates a Dataset with a Platform, indicating which satellite or platform collected the dataset.

Label: HAS_SCIENCEKEYWORD
Description: Links a Dataset to a ScienceKeyword, categorizing the dataset by its scientific domain and application.

Label: HAS_SUBCATEGORY
Description: Defines hierarchical relationships between ScienceKeyword nodes, representing parent-child relationships in the keyword taxonomy.

Label: landingPageUrl
Description: The URL of the primary landing page or homepage for accessing detailed information about the resource.

Label: nwCorner_crs
Description: The coordinate reference system for the northwest corner of the dataset's spatial coverage.

Label: nwCorner_latitude
Description: The latitude coordinate of the northwest corner of the dataset's spatial coverage bounding box.

Label: nwCorner_longitude
Description: The longitude coordinate of the northwest corner of the dataset's spatial coverage bounding box.

Label: OF_PROJECT
Description: Links a Dataset to a Project, indicating which scientific mission or project the dataset belongs to.

Label: pagerank_publication_dataset
Description: A computed PageRank value indicating the importance or centrality of publication-dataset relationships in the graph.

Label: seCorner_crs
Description: The coordinate reference system for the southeast corner of the dataset's spatial coverage.

Label: seCorner_latitude
Description: The latitude coordinate of the southeast corner of the dataset's spatial coverage bounding box.

Label: seCorner_longitude
Description: The longitude coordinate of the southeast corner of the dataset's spatial coverage bounding box.

Label: temporalFrequency
Description: The frequency at which data is collected or observations are made (e.g., daily, hourly, unknown).

Label: Type
Description: Specifies the type or classification of the resource within the knowledge graph schema.

Label: url
Description: A URL providing direct access to the resource or additional information about it.

Label: USES_DATASET
Description: Connects a Publication to a Dataset, indicating that the publication references or utilizes data from that dataset.

Label: abstract
Description: A summary or abstract describing the content and purpose of the resource (Schema.org).

Label: title
Description: The name or title of the resource (Schema.org).
